 \"dozens\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"nations\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple events\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The three main \\\"events\\\" to watch in the Space Olympics are the competitions in commercial space, military space, and lunar exploration.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The three main \\\"events\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"the Space Olympics\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitions\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"commercial space\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"military space\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"lunar exploration\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stakes are highest in these events because nations are competing to build an enduring economic and military advantage-and shape the de facto rules for how the space economy will operate in the future.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The stakes\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"these events\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"nations\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"an enduring economic and military advantage\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1581}, {\"ngram\": \"the de facto rules\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"the space economy\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1636}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Below is your guide to each of these competitions explaining what is at stake, how the competition is shaping up, and which nations are favored to win.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your guide\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"these competitions\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"stake\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\